# Khurik, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Khurik (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative centre of  Khuriksky Selsoviet, Tabasaransky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 8 streets.
Geography
By road, Khurik is located 8&nbsp;km northwest of Khuchni (the district's administrative centre). Rugudzh is the nearest rural locality.
